# node_modules is intentionally NOT excluded — with skip_api_build=true
# on the SWA deploy action, we pre-build in CI and the Function App runs
# directly from the uploaded bundle. If node_modules is stripped here,
# the Function App boots but every function throws
# "Cannot find module '@azure/functions'".
